HaHa. I now reveal my true face.....It's me, I'm back
again! I told you I'd be back. It's Halloween part 5,
Jasons back and he's pissed off! Dachande on the cover
of News Week is kinda like Hannibal on the cover of
Gourmet Cooking. Not a good thing. Anywho, I will be
reclaiming my characters: Magmatron, Optimus Prime,
Cerberus, and Dachande. Then I have the new and cool
NightBlade. So Battera is now in the hands of Alloran?
Well, okay, that's going to be weird. Just lettin
everybody know that I'm back. And I will probably be
posting from my old e-mail soon, but until then, this
is the one I use.
